# SKYETECH Sovereign Primitives — App Functions

## Purpose
This file is the straight app/function registry for the sovereign stack. It is intentionally focused on **what each app or security surface does right now**.

It is **not** the upgrade plan. The upgrade and integration planning belongs in `Cross-Platform-Architecture`.

---

